@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Magic Mirror";
}

<div class="cepha-hero">
    <h1>🪞 Magic Mirror — المرآة السحرية</h1>
    <p class="lead">The web layer — fonts + the <strong>gpt-oss-20b</strong> Sarmad gateway for the native overlay.</p>
    <p class="text-muted">ASP.NET MVC running entirely in WebAssembly with <strong>NetWasmMvc.SDK</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class="cepha-features">
    <div class="cepha-card">
        <div class="cepha-card-body">
            <h3>🤖 AI gateway</h3>
            <p>Deploys <code>POST /api/sarmad/ask</code> on Cloudflare Pages, routed to Cloudflare
               Workers AI <code>@@cf/openai/gpt-oss-20b</code>. The native mirror calls it to
               translate captured text.</p>
            <span class="cepha-chip cepha-chip-success">CephaSarmadPlatform</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cepha-card">
        <div class="cepha-card-body">
            <h3>🔤 Fonts</h3>
            <p>Serves Arabic-capable fonts so the overlay can match the original text's family,
               weight and size.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cepha-card">
        <div class="cepha-card-body">
            <h3>🖥️ Native overlay</h3>
            <p>A MAUI sibling app (generated by <code>cepha native-app</code>) captures any window,
               OCRs the text, and paints the translation on top — Windows now, Android next.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cepha-card">
        <div class="cepha-card-body">
            <h3>🌙 Main language</h3>
            <p>Translates into the configured main language (Arabic by default), with slight
               dimming so the translation reads clearly over the original.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="cepha-panel cepha-panel-info" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
    <p>Deploy this layer with <code>cepha publish cf</code>, then set the native app's
       <strong>AI gateway base URL</strong> to this site so translations use
       <code>@@cf/openai/gpt-oss-20b</code>. Without a deploy, translation uses MT fallback and
       dictionary analysis remains unavailable until a real gateway is configured.</p>
</div>
